caption:
Last week, we had an amazing time in New York, handing out new shoes to local elementary school kids with our partners at Nordstrom.

Since 2010, @nordstrom and @nordstromrack, with the support of their customers, have helped us provide shoes to over 380,000 kids. 

There’s still time to be part of this year’s incredible campaign! Through October 19, you can donate and help us reach our goal of giving shoes to 50,000 more children this fall. 

Visit shoesthatfit.org/nordstrom to donate today! 👟🧡 #ShoesThatFit #Nordstrom #ForTheKids #CommunityImpact
